Bring a large pot of salted water to boil. In a large skillet, saute salmon in 1 tablespoon of the olive oil for 2 minutes and set aside. Heat olive oil in a large skillet; add scallions and cherry tomatoes, saut√© 2-3 minutes. Add lemon juice. Season with salt and pepper. Cook PLUS(R) Rotini according to package directions. During last 2 minutes of cook time, add asparagus. Drain and immediately add to sauce. Add tarragon, mix well. Add salmon and toss gently. May be served warm or cold as a salad.